These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, davidoff, ritmeester, blend, dannemann
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, rose, dahlia, begonia, tulip
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
7. the blend-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | aristoff  | davidoff    | ritmeester  | alhambra      | blend    |
| Flower      | iris  | tulip | begonia | daffodil | dahlia | rose |

