.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, basketball, handball, rugby, biathlon
The people use 6 different means of transport: ship, trike, car, tram, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the train##1
8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
9. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Sport   | water-polo   | rugby | weightlifting | biathlon | handball     | basketball  |
| Transport           | car | trike    | ship      | train  | tram | motorbike |

