.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, roller, tram, trike, subway
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, musical, disaster, animation, time-travel
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching musical movies is the person driving the tram##1
9. the person driving the roller is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Transport   | tram   | subway   | trike      | skateboard | motorbike  | roller   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | time-travel | mystery | thriller   | animation | disaster |

