.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, russian, japanese, malaysian, french, argentine
City: liverpool, edinburgh, nizza, miami, new-york, berlin
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
2. the japanese is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the argentine is on the left of the french##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is the malaysian##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
7. the french is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Nationality   | japanese  | malaysian | indonesian      | russian  | argentine | french |
| City     | liverpool | berlin  | new-york | nizza | miami  | edinburgh    |

