.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, ship, skateboard, subway, taxi
There are 6 different favourite colors: blue, orange, light-blue, ebony, fuchsia, grey
 1. the person who likes light-blue is the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Transport         | skateboard | taxi | bus | subway | motorbike | ship  |
| Color   | grey  | ebony  | light-blue  | blue | fuchsia      | orange |

