.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, chess, canasta, domino, go
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca, baccarat, montecristo, cain, pall-mall
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the cain-smoker is the person playing go##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Game   | go    | chess    | mah-jongg | domino     | monopoly   | canasta     |
| Cigar   | cain | fonseca | pall-mall | baccarat | montecristo | old-henry |

