.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, september, october, august, november, april
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, lemonade, fanta, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Birthday         | september       | april     | august | october | november | june |
| Beverage   | tea | mirinda | soy-milk | lemonade     | milk  | fanta       |

