.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
6 different pets are kept: horse, cat, rabbit, dog, fish, guinea-pig
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bluemaster, bongani, chaman, baccarat, alhambra
1. the owner of the rabbit is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the dog##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | horse  | fish     | rabbit    | cat  | dog          |
| Cigar         | bluemaster  | aristoff | bongani | baccarat | chaman | alhambra |

