There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, german, malaysian, argentine, turkish, french
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the german##1
4. the french is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the indonesian##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Sport    | tennis | skiing | weightlifting | biathlon    | ice-hockey | rugby      |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | indonesian     | german      | turkish | french           | argentine |

