.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
6 different games are played: chess, canasta, snooker, poker, bridge, mah-jongg
The people have 6 different jobs:  fisherman, electrician, security-guard, photographer, dancer, accountant
1. the fisherman is on the right of the electrician##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
3. the electrician is the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the dancer##1
5. the photographer is on the far right##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the fisherman##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the security-guard##1
9. the security-guard is on the left of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Game          | canasta | mah-jongg   | bridge  | snooker    | poker  | chess |
| Job   | electrician   | fisherman | accountant | dancer | security-guard | photographer |

