.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: soul, r&b, trance, pop, d&b, ambient
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, december, may, april, july, january
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
7. the fan of soul is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | soul     | trance | r&b | pop | d&b   |
| Birthday        | january | april | july | may   | october    | december |

