3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Birthday   | june | may | december    | november | february  | march |
| Movie-Genre     | satire    | martial-arts | superhero | horror   | crime | scientific    |

