3. the person playing bridge is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking bridgeade##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing go##1
9. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Game        | bridge     | whist | go   | scrabble      | mah-jongg | monopoly |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate  | iced-tea | bridgeade | fanta   | coffee     |

