.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, april, september, july, march, may
6 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, turtle, hamster, goat, dog
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
9. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Birthday   | april | may     | march       | september  | july | december    |
| Pet     | dog  | lizard | mouse | hamster | goat  | turtle |

 